name: Prophet
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Prophet Token is a yield farming token that is minted and distributed to liquidity providers on OracleSwap.io.
Prophet Token has a built in 1% burn to reduce the inflationary effect of the yield farm.
The PRO multistaking system allows PRO to be staked/locked to earn a multiplicity of ERC-20 token types as well as LP token pairs.
